Maintainer: Gerald KERMA <devel@cybermind.fr>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13)
Standards-Version: 4.6.2

Package: secubox-ipblock
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, secubox-core (>= 1.0.0), nftables, curl
Description: SecuBox IP Blocklist Manager
 IP blocklist management module for SecuBox.
 Features include:
  - Multiple blocklist sources (Spamhaus, AbuseIPDB, FireHOL, etc.)
  - Custom blocklist rules
  - nftables set integration
  - Whitelist management
  - Auto-update scheduling
  - Block statistics and history
  - Import/export lists
